Madam President, I would like to know if this week Parliament will send out a clear signal of our dissatisfaction with today's decision to reject an extension of the arms embargo against Indonesia, especially since the vast majority in this Parliament has in the past voted for it Has imposed an arms embargo on Indonesia.
